---
/** Tummy time: three easy positions and how the daily amount builds up. */
---

<figure class="diagram">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 720 330" width="100%" fill="none" role="img" aria-label="Tummy time: three positions — on a floor mat, on your chest, or across your lap — starting at 3 to 5 minutes a few times a day and building to 15–30 minutes a day by around 7 weeks.">
    <rect width="720" height="330" rx="16" fill="var(--sage-wash, #E8F0E3)" />

    <g font-family="var(--font-body)">
      <!-- Position 1: floor mat -->
      <g>
        <rect x="52" y="60" width="180" height="110" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" />
        <rect x="72" y="140" width="140" height="10" rx="5" fill="var(--leaf, #8FBC85)" />
        <circle cx="102" cy="122" r="13" fill="var(--butter, #F2DFA8)" />
        <path d="M114 128 Q150 116 178 130 Q186 136 178 140 L120 138 Z" fill="var(--leaf, #8FBC85)" />
        <path d="M96 116 q4 -8 12 -4" stroke="var(--ink, #3D443A)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" />
        <text x="142" y="196" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">On a floor mat</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Position 2: on your chest -->
      <g>
        <rect x="270" y="60" width="180" height="110" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" />
        <path d="M300 156 Q306 108 348 96 L390 88 Q414 88 420 104 L424 156 Z" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" />
        <circle cx="394" cy="76" r="14" fill="var(--butter, #F2DFA8)" />
        <circle cx="342" cy="102" r="11" fill="var(--butter, #F2DFA8)" />
        <path d="M352 108 Q374 104 392 112 L390 122 L354 118 Z" fill="var(--leaf, #8FBC85)" />
        <text x="360" y="196" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">On your chest</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Position 3: across your lap -->
      <g>
        <rect x="488" y="60" width="180" height="110" rx="14" fill="#FFFFFF" />
        <rect x="508" y="132" width="60" height="18" rx="9" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" />
        <rect x="588" y="132" width="60" height="18" rx="9" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" />
        <circle cx="530" cy="116" r="12" fill="var(--butter, #F2DFA8)" />
        <path d="M542 120 Q580 108 618 122 L616 132 L544 130 Z" fill="var(--leaf, #8FBC85)" />
        <text x="578" y="196" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14.5" font-weight="700" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">Across your lap</text>
      </g>

      <!-- Build-up bar -->
      <rect x="52" y="232" width="616" height="20" rx="10" fill="#FFFFFF" />
      <rect x="52" y="232" width="150" height="20" rx="10" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" />
      <rect x="52" y="232" width="430" height="20" rx="10" fill="var(--sage, #6B9A5F)" opacity="0.35" />
      <text x="52" y="286" font-size="14" font-weight="700" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">Start: 3–5 min, 2–3× a day</text>
      <text x="668" y="286" text-anchor="end" font-size="14" font-weight="700" fill="var(--ink, #3D443A)">By ~7 weeks: 15–30 min per day</text>
      <text x="360" y="312" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13.5" fill="var(--ink-soft, #68715F)">Always awake, always supervised — never for sleep.</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption>Three ways in, tiny doses, building up — tummy time is a workout, and protests are normal. (AAP &amp; CPS.)</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .diagram {
    margin: var(--space-2) 0;
  }

  .diagram figcaption {
    margin-top: var(--space-half);
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
</style>
